    <section id="Apache+Allura+Project+Incubation+Status">
      <title>Apache Allura Project Incubation Status</title>
      <p>This page tracks the project status, incubator-wise. For more general
        project status, look on the <a href="https://forge-allura.apache.org/p/allura/">project website</a>.</p>
      <p><span class='graduated'>The Allura project graduated on 2014-03-19</span></p>
    </section>
    <section id="Description">
      <title>Description</title>
      <p>Apache Allura is a software "forge", a
        web site that manages source code repositories,
        bug reports, discussions, wiki pages, blogs and
        more for any number of individual projects.</p>
    </section>
